# Note: The list of ForEachMacros can be obtained using:
#
#    git grep -h '^#define [^[:space:]]*FOR_EACH[^[:space:]]*(' include/ \
#    | sed "s,^#define \([^[:space:]]*FOR_EACH[^[:space:]]*\)(.*$,  - '\1'," \
#    | sort | uniq
#
# References:
#   - https://clang.llvm.org/docs/ClangFormatStyleOptions.html

---
BasedOnStyle: LLVM